TEXT.TITLE: OUTBOARD MARINE <OM> KNOWS NO REASON STOCK IS UP
TEXT.BODY: Outboard Marine Corp, whose stock is trading higher, said there were no corporate developments to account for the rise. Outboard Marine was up 2-1/2 to 34 with 48,000 shares traded. A spokesman said the company wasn't planning any announcements. Several analysts who follow the company also did not know why Outboard was trading higher. Reuter
